             was indicted <rs id="t18200918-15-off78" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18200918-15-off78" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200918-15-off78" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               for stealing, on the <rs id="t18200918-15-cd79" type="crimeDate">9th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200918-15-off78 t18200918-15-cd79"></join>, at St. James, Westminster, one hat, value 1 l., and one box, value 6 d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18200918-15-victim202" type="victimName">
                           James 
                           Swallow
                        <interp inst="t18200918-15-victim202" type="surname" value="Swallow"></interp>
